@wp.kernel
def expr_hxuycm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v2 = ((0.02 * wp.sin(v1 + 0.91)) / 0.9)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.34)) / (tmp + (v0 + 0.34 - v2 + 0.43)))
    v0 = wp.cos(0.15)
    v2 = v2
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.11)))
    tmp = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v2 + 0.01 * v1 + 0.04)))
    v2 = 0.78
    data[tid] = v0
